{"prompt": "Generate a website for a online magazine. The website should be futuristic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Chrono Magazine</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #0a1f3a;\n            --secondary-blue: #1a3a5a;\n            --accent-blue: #3a6abf;\n            --text-color: #e0e0e0;\n            --background-dark: #050d15;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-dark);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-blue), 0 0 20px var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/0a1f3a/ffffff?text=Future+Explorations') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 31, 58, 0.8), rgba(26, 58, 90, 0.8));\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(10, 18, 30, 0.7);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(58, 106, 191, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            color: #c0c0c0;\n        }\n\n        .articles {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .article-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        .article-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(58, 106, 191, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .article-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n            filter: brightness(0.9);\n        }\n\n        .article-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .article-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        .article-content p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #d0d0d0;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .article-content a {\n            color: var(--accent-blue);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .article-content a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--accent-blue);\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #a0a0a0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            .articles {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Chrono Magazine</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#\">Home</a>\n                <a href=\"#\">Technology</a>\n                <a href=\"#\">Science</a>\n                <a href=\"#\">Culture</a>\n                <a href=\"#\">About</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Exploring Tomorrow, Today</h2>\n            <p>Your portal to the cutting edge of innovation and futuristic thought.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <main class=\"articles\">\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/3a6abf/ffffff?text=AI+Evolution\" alt=\"AI Evolution\">\n                <div class=\"article-content\">\n                    <h3>The Next Leap in Artificial Intelligence</h3>\n                    <p>Discover the advancements that are reshaping our understanding of machine intelligence.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/1a3a5a/ffffff?text=Space+Frontiers\" alt=\"Space Frontiers\">\n                <div class=\"article-content\">\n                    <h3>Unlocking New Space Frontiers</h3>\n                    <p>From Mars colonization to interstellar travel, the cosmos is calling.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/0a1f3a/ffffff?text=Bio-Tech\" alt=\"Bio-Tech\">\n                <div class=\"article-content\">\n                    <h3>Revolutionary Bio-Tech Innovations</h3>\n                    <p>How genetic engineering and synthetic biology are changing life as we know it.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/3a6abf/ffffff?text=Digital+Realms\" alt=\"Digital Realms\">\n                <div class=\"article-content\">\n                    <h3>The Metaverse and Digital Realities</h3>\n                    <p>Navigating the immersive worlds of virtual and augmented reality.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n        </main>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2077 Chrono Magazine. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}